** Residue Theorem

#+BEGIN_EXPORT latex
\begin{theorem}
  Suppose $f:U\subseteq \mathbb{C}\to \mathbb{C}$ is holomorphic on $U\setminus\{a_1,...,a_n\}$. $U$ an open set then we have that
  \begin{align*}
    \int_U f(z)\dd z = 2\pi i \sum_{k=1}^n \text{Res}\qty(f,a_k)
  \end{align*}
\end{theorem}
#+END_EXPORT

